metadata.name: I am Ukrainian.
metadata.description:
This object or art was born during performance. This painting has its own history. This is the cry of my soul. Every word and charcoal stroke is a reflection of my inner emotions. The ones that tear my soul apart. 
50% proceeds from this collection will be donated to ''mashafund'' supporting Ukrainian children and women. 



*Upon purchase NFT, collector will receive the original painting 
directly to address.
